Bower.

    - bower is the Automation tool used to download the Required Resources to Develop web application.

    - bower is the tool given by the nodejs.


bower components.

1.bower.json
2. .bowerrc


bower.json
-
{
    "name":"nareshit",
    "dependencies":{
        "angular":"~1.6.0",
        "bootstrap":"~3.3.6"
    }
}


.bowerrc.

    - used to locate the path to resources downloading by bower.

{
    "directory":"bower_component"
}






